<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <!-- <title>
        Your Carbon Footprint :
    </title> -->
    <style>
        table {
            width: 50%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 0 auto;
            /* Center the table */
        }

        table,
        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid black;
        }

        th,
        td {
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div style="padding: 20px 0;">

        <div>
            <img src="https://carbon-emissions-pnz7.onrender.com/logo/logo4.gif" width="30%" />
            <!-- <img src="logo4.gif" width="100%" /> -->
        </div>
        <h4>Dear <%= name %>,</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;">Thank you for using Siratâ€™s<strong>NetZero Platfrom</strong>to measure the carbon
            footprint generated from
            your <strong>
                <%= activityName %>
            </strong>activity. We deeply value your
            commitment
            to
            sustainability and appreciate your proactive approach in understanding and mitigating your environmental
            impact.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;">We're pleased to provide you with the carbon footprint report, detailing the
            emissions associated with the above
            mentioned activity.</p>
        <h2 style="text-align: center;">Total Carbon Footprint :</h2>

        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Air Travel</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalAirTravel %> kgco<sub>2</sub>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Local Transportation</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalLocalTransportation %> kgco<sub>2</sub>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Hotel</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalHotel %> kgco<sub>2</sub>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Food</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalFood %> kgco<sub>2</sub>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Logistics</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalAirFreight %> kgco<sub>2</sub>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Event Production</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totlaProduction %> kgco<sub>2</sub>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Energy</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalEnergyUpdated %> kgco<sub>2</sub>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Digital</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalDIgitalContent %> kgco<sub>2</sub>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Waste</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalWaste %> kgco<sub>2</sub>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <h4 class=''>Total = <%= data.grandTotal %> kgco<sub>2</sub></h4>
        <h4 class=''>Total tCO2e = <%= totalTonCo2 %> tCO<sub>2</sub>e</h4>

        <h4>For every $ you spend you are generating <%= eveydolarCo2 %> kgco<sub>2</sub></h4>

        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance on how to reduce the carbon emissions, please contact at
            <a href="info@sirat.earth" target="_blank">info@sirat.earth</a>
            . We are here to help you on your journey towards a more sustainable future.
        </p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0;">Team Sirat</p>
        <a style="text-decoration:underline;color: blue;">Sirat.Earth</a>

    </div>
</body>

</html>